#Section 1 (This is the monthly (or less often) additions to pool. Side 0
#means Japanese SCPs are used, side 1 means Allied SCPs. Amount is how many
#ships of the next slot_xxx is being tried to add. Slot_xxx is just the
#default for reference. And the times are really complex, so I haven't
#placed them here, you'll just have to make do with slots and amounts.
#It should be safe to make Amount 0, effectively disabling that slot.)
#
#Shippool is added to on the first week of the month.
#
#Following shipslots get new ships, if ship constructions points allow.
#(And the full cost of (number*(dur+arm)) must be available, and spent.)
#If not, no ships of that slot are added to pool that month.
#Also, the side whose scp's are used, is mentioned here.
#(And this is the order they are in the code, not easy to modify
#systematically.)
#
#Japanese scps:
#Slot 154 gets 4/month, until March '44.
#Slot 154 gets 15/month, starting April '44.
#(Slot 154's both use the same slot_154 line.)
#Slot 191 gets 1/month, during '44.
#Slot 192 gets 1/month, during '45.
#Slot 182 gets 2/month, during Jan-Sep, starting '43.
#Slot 183 gets 2/month, during Oct-Dec, starting '43.
#Slot 182 gets 3 more/month, during Apr-Dec, starting '44.
#Slot 183 gets 3 more/month, during Jan-Mar, starting '44.
#Slot 179 gets 12/month.
#Slot 180 gets 3/month.
#Slot 179 gets 12 more/every 2 months, starting '44.
#Slot 180 gets 12 more/every 2 months, starting '44.
#Slot 181 gets 1/every 3 months.
#Slot 168 gets 4/month.
#Slot 169 gets 1/month.
#Slot 170 gets 1/every 6 months.
#Slot 165 gets 1/every 6 months.
#
#Allied scps:
#Slot 156 gets 8/month, during Jul-Dec '42.
#Slot 156 gets 8/month, in '43, if there are less than 41 in pool.
#(Slot 156 getting 8 are both on the same line (slot_156_8).) 
#Slot 156 gets 16/month, starting '44, if there are less than 81 in pool.
#Slot 166 gets 2/every 2 months.
#Slot 186 gets 2/every 2 months.
#Slot 171 gets 4/month, starting September '42.
#Slot 172 gets 6/every 2 months, starting '43.
#Slot 173 gets 2/every 2 months, starting '44.
#Slot 184 gets 2/month, during '42-'43.
#Slot 184 gets 6/every 2 months, starting '44.
#Slot 185 gets 2/every 2 months.
#Slot 157 gets 1/every 3 months, until '44.
#Slot 159 gets 1/month, starting '44.
#Slot 177 gets 10/month, starting May '43.
#Slot 195 gets 2/every 2 months, until '43.
#Slot 195 gets 6/every 2 months, during '43.
#Slot 195 gets 10/every 2 months, starting '44.
#Slot 197 gets 2/every 4 months, during '43.
#Slot 197 gets 2/every 2 months, starting '44.
#(Slot 197's are both handled by the same line.)
#Slot 187 gets 2/every 2 months.
#Slot 188 gets 1/every 2 months.
#Slot 189 gets 1/every 2 months.
#Slot 174 gets 6/every 2 months, during '45.
#Slot 175 gets 4/every 2 months, during '45.
#Slot 176 gets 2/every 2 months, during '45.
#Slot 178 gets 8/every 2 months, during '45.
#Slot 167 gets 2/every 2 months, during '45.

